value.value: Catalysis of the reaction: glutathionate + L-gamma-glutamyl-L-cysteinyl-beta-alaninate = gamma-Glu-Cys-gamma-Glu-Cys-beta-Ala + glycine.
Catalysis of the reaction: H2O + a glutathione-toxin conjugate = glycine + a [Glu-Cys]-S-conjugate.
Catalysis of the reaction: malonyl-CoA(5-) + an L-cysteine-S-conjugate = coenzyme A + H+ + an N-malonyl-L-cysteine-S-conjugate.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2-oxoglutarate(2-) + O2 + 2 H+ = ethene + 3 carbon dioxide + H2O.
Catalysis of the reaction: beta-D-glucosaminyl-(1->4)-N-acetyl-D-glucosamine + H2O = D-glucosamine + N-acetyl-D-glucosamine.
Catalysis of the reaction: choline + NADP+ = betaine aldehyde + NADPH + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: formylaminopyrimidine + H2O = 4-amino-5-ammoniomethyl-2-methylpyrimidine + formate.
Catalysis of the reaction: 1-deoxy-11-oxopentalenate + O2 + NADPH + H+ = pentalenolactone D + H2O + NADP.
Catalysis of the reaction: L-ornithinium(1+) = N(5)-acetyl-L-ornithine.
Catalysis of the reaction: 4-coumaryl-CoA + 3-oxooctanoyl-CoA + H2O = 4-coumaroylhexanoylmethane + 2 coenzyme A + carbon dioxide.
Catalysis of the reaction: beta-amyrin + 2 O2 + 2 NADPH + 2 H+ = 11-oxo-beta-amyrin + 3 H2O + 2 NADP.
Catalysis of the reaction: 30-hydroxy-beta-amyrin + O2 + NADPH + H+ = 11alpha,30-dihydroxy-beta-amyrin + H2O + NADP.
Catalysis of the reaction: cholesterol + NAD = cholest-5-en-3-one + NADH + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 4-methylumbelliferyl glucoside + malonyl-CoA = 4-methylumbelliferone 6'-O-malonylglucoside + coenzyme A.

Catalysis of the reaction: (1E,2Z)-3-hydroxy-5,9,17-trioxo-4,5:9,10-disecoandrosta-1(10),2-dien-4-oate + H2O = 9,17-dioxo-1,2,3,4,10,19-hexanorandrostan-5-oate + (2Z,4Z)-2-hydroxyhexa-2,4-dienoate + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: selenic acid + ATP + 2 H+ = adenylyl selenate + diphosphoric acid.
Catalysis of the reaction: L-selenocysteine + O-phosphonato-L-homoserine = hydrogenphosphate + L-selenocystathionine.

Catalysis of the reaction: (9Z,12Z,15Z)-octadecatrienoate + O2 = (9R,10E,12Z,15Z)-9-hydroperoxyoctadeca-10,12,15-trienoate. Also converts linoleate to (9R,10E,12Z)-9- hydroperoxyoctadeca-10,12-dienoate.
Catalysis of the reaction: malonyl-CoA + gamma-linolenoyl-CoA + H+ = (8Z,11Z,14Z)-3-oxoicosa-8,11,14-trienoyl-CoA + coenzyme A + carbon dioxide.
Catalysis of the reaction: S-adenosyl-L-methionine + mycinamicin VI = S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + mycinamicin III(1+) + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2 S-adenosyl-L-methionine + trans-resveratrol = 2 S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + pterostilbene + 2 H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2-trans,6-trans-farnesyl diphosphate(3-) = 7-epi-sesquithujene + diphosphoric acid.
Catalysis of the reaction: geranylgeranyl diphosphate + H2O = (13E)-labda-7,13-dien-15-ol + diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: (S)-benzoin + NADP(3-) = benzil + NADPH(4-) + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: erythromycin C + S-adenosyl-L-methionine = erythromycin A + H+ + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine. Also converts erythromycin D into erythromycin B.
Catalysis of the reaction: dTDP-4-dehydro-2,6-dideoxy-alpha-D-allose + NAD(P) = dTDP-(2R,6S)-6-hydroxy-2-methyl-3-oxo-3,6-dihydro-2H-pyran-4-olate + 2 H+ + NAD(P)H.
Catalysis of the reaction: (6E)-8-hydroxygeraniol + 2 NADP = (6E)-8-oxogeranial + 2 NADPH + 2 H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 4-coumaryl-CoA + 2-oxoglutarate + O2 = 2,4-dihydroxycinnamoyl-CoA + succinate + carbon dioxide.
Catalysis of the reaction: geranyl diphosphate(3-) + H2O = 1,8-cineole + diphosphoric acid.
Catalysis of the reaction: 4-(methylamino)butyric acid + O2 + H2O = gamma-aminobutyric acid + formaldehyde + hydrogen peroxide.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2-deoxystreptamine + UDP-alpha-D-glucose = 2'-deamino-2'-hydroxyparomamine + UDP(3-) + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2-deoxystreptamine(2+) + UDP-N-acetyl-alpha-D-glucosamine = H+ + 2'-N-acetylparomamine(2+) + UDP(3-).
Catalysis of the reaction: 1,8-cineole + NADPH + H+ + O2 = 2-exo-hydroxy-1,8-cineole + NADP + H2O.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2-propylphenol + O2 + NADH + H+ = 3-propylcatechol + H2O + NAD.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2-isopropylphenol + O2 + NADH + H+ = 3-isopropylcatechol + H2O + NAD.
Catalysis of the reaction: biphenyl-2,2',3-triol + O2 + NADH + H+ = 2,2',3,3'-tetrahydroxybiphenyl + NAD + H2O.
Catalysis of the reaction: malonyl-CoA + a palmitoyl-[acp] = 1-heptadecene + 2 carbon dioxide + coenzyme A + a holo-[acyl-carrier protein].
Catalysis of the reaction: malonyl-CoA + 3 H+ + a heptodecanoyl-[acp] = octadec-1-ene + 2 carbon dioxide + coenzyme A + a holo-[acyl-carrier protein].

Catalysis of the reaction: malonyl-CoA + H+ + a long-chain acyl-[acp] + a reduced electron acceptor = 2 carbon dioxide + coenzyme A + a terminal olefin + a holo-[acyl-carrier protein] + an oxidized electron acceptor.
Catalysis of the reaction: malonyl-CoA + 3 H+ + a stearoyl-[acp] = nonadec-1-ene + 2 carbon dioxide + coenzyme A + a holo-[acyl-carrier protein].
Catalysis of the reaction: ditrans,polycis-undecaprenyl phosphate + UDP-N,N'-diacetylbacillosamine = N,N'-diacetyl-alpha-D-bacillosaminyl-diphospho-tri-trans,hepta-cis-undecaprenol + UMP.

Catalysis of the reaction: N,N'-diacetyl-alpha-D-bacillosaminyl-diphospho-tri-trans,hepta-cis-undecaprenol + UDP-N-acetyl-D-galactosamine = N-acetyl-D-galactosaminyl-alpha-(1->3)-N,N'-diacetyl-alpha-D-bacillosaminyl-diphospho-tri-trans,hepta-cis-undecaprenol + UDP + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: ATP + a 1,2-diacyl-sn-glycerol 3-phosphate = ADP + a 1,2-diacyl-sn-glycerol 3-diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: 11-cis-retinol + NADP = 11-cis-retinal + NADPH + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2-oxo-3-(5-oxofuran-2-ylidene)propanoate + H2O = 3-maleylpyruvate + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2-trans,6-trans-farnesyl diphosphate(3-) = diphosphoric acid + (+)-isoitalicene.
Catalysis of the reaction: mithramycin + NADP = mithramycin DK + NADPH + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 7,8-dihydroxycoumarin + S-adenosyl-L-methionine = 7-hydroxy-8-methoxycoumarin + H+ + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine.
Catalysis of the reaction: isoscopoletin + S-adenosyl-L-methionine = scoparone + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: taxusin + NADPH + O2 + H+ = 2-alpha-hydroxytaxusin + NADP + H2O. Also converts 7beta-hydroxytaxusin to 2alpha,7beta-dihydroxytaxusin.
